FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779843788
OL,3,CSpy chief to warn of 'relentless'
OL,4,CRussian cyber attacks on UK and Europe
OL,6,FShe is expected to highlight the
OL,7,Forganisation's efforts in "disrupting
OL,8,FRussia's efforts to smuggle western
OL,9,Ftech, fending off cyber attacks, and
OL,10,Fcountering reckless sabotage and
OL,11,Fassassination attempts", adding, "as
OL,12,Fwe remain steadfast in our support for
OL,13,FUkraine, Putin is going backwards on
OL,14,Fthe battlefield".
OL,26,@oD@[OUsD@WO]sD@bOUvD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
