FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779843788
OL,3,CSpy chief to warn of 'relentless'
OL,4,CRussian cyber attacks on UK and Europe
OL,6,FRussia is "relentlessly targeting
OL,7,Fcritical infrastructure, democratic
OL,8,Fprocesses, supply chains and public
OL,9,Ftrust", she is expected to tell the
OL,10,Faudience, and the speed of
OL,11,Fadvancements in technology mean there
OL,12,Fis a "narrowing window for the UK and
OL,13,Fallies to stay ahead", she will say.
OL,15,F"China is now a science and tech
OL,16,Fsuperpower, with sophisticated
OL,17,Fcapabilities across their
OL,18,Fintelligence, cyber and military
OL,19,Fagencies", and rapid progression in AI
OL,20,Fmeans "the ground beneath our feet is
OL,21,Fshifting", the audience will hear.
OL,26,@nD@KOUqD@FO]tD@FOUuD@UO]wD@AOU{D@IO]|D@
OL,26,AGOU}D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
