OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779843788
OL,3,CSpy chief to warn of 'relentless'
OL,4,CRussian cyber attacks on UK and Europe
OL,6,FShe will urge the technology industry
OL,7,Fand those working in national security
OL,8,Fto "anticipate and drive advancements,
OL,9,Ftogether, at the speed of the
OL,10,Ffrontier", as well as calling on the
OL,11,Fpublic to take action "from boardrooms
OL,12,Fto living rooms" to increase cyber
OL,13,Fsecurity.
OL,15,F"At home, that means taking important
OL,16,Faction now to switch passwords for
OL,17,Fpasskeys, and for wider society, it
OL,18,Fmeans hardwiring security into new
OL,19,Ftechnologies, protecting supply chains
OL,20,Fand making cyber security 10 times
OL,21,Fmore urgent," she will say.
OL,26,@pD@DOUrD@IO]sD@WOUtD@PO]wD@AOU}D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
