OL,3,CSpy chief to warn of 'relentless'
OL,4,CRussian cyber attacks on UK and Europe
OL,6,FEarlier this year, Dr Richard Horne,
OL,7,Fhead of the National Cyber Security
OL,8,FCentre which is part of GCHQ, warned
OL,9,Fthat most nationally significant cyber
OL,10,Fattacks on Britain were carried out by
OL,11,Fhostile states including China, Iran
OL,12,Fand Russia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779843788
OL,3,CSpy chief to warn of 'relentless'
OL,4,CRussian cyber attacks on UK and Europe
OL,6,FHe said the body dealt with around
OL,7,Ffour of these attacks each week, and
OL,8,Fwarned businesses to be prepared to
OL,9,Fprotect themselves against cyber
OL,10,Fattacks without needing the option of
OL,11,Fpaying ransoms, because the UK could
OL,12,Fbe targeted "at scale" if it were to
OL,13,Fbecome involved in an international
OL,14,Fconflict.
OL,26,@tD@MOUtD@VO]
